Jane Wanjuki Njiru bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Kenya
Ọ bụ onye nnọchi anya ụmụ nwanyị nke Embu County na onye otu ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị na-achị, otu Jubilee nke Kenya. Ọ gbara mpi ma merie ọkwa onye nnọchi anya nwanyị Embu na ntuli aka ọra nke afọ 2017.
Ọ gara ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị Mulango Girls maka asambodo agụmakwụkwọ Kenya na 1971 ruo 1974

Ọ gara n'ihu na agụmakwụkwọ ya na Kenya Management and Training Institute ebe ọ nwetara Advanced Diploma in management, Advance Diploma in Sale and Marketing and Diploma in Public Relations. Ọ bụ osote onye isi oche ọhụrụ nke kọmitii nkwukọrịta, ozi na Innovation na ndị omeiwu. Ọ bụ onye otu Kọmitii Ngalaba na-ahụ maka ala na mmejuputa iwu na 12th parliament.

A họpụtara Njiru dị ka onye nnọchi anya ụmụ nwanyị nke Embu County na 2017. Ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị ka Chief Executive Officer na New day Motors Limited na 2006 ruo 2017 na 1979 ruo 2006 ọ bụ Sales and Marketing Associate na Telecom Kenya.
